          <para><link linkend="vcopy_i"><citetitle>vcopy_i</citetitle></link></para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
  </para>
  <para>
    All these operators are designed to be used together with other opcodes that operate with vectorial signals such as <link linkend="vcella"><citetitle>vcella</citetitle></link>, <link linkend="adsynt"><citetitle>adsynt</citetitle></link>, <link linkend="adsynt2"><citetitle>adsynt2</citetitle></link>, etc.
  </para>
